<subSubSection box="[199,1251,834,859]" pageId="3" pageNumber="207" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,438,859]" box="[199,1251,834,859]" pageId="3" pageNumber="207">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,835,859]" pageId="3" pageNumber="207">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is based on a comparison to 
<taxonomicName box="[776,876,835,859]" class="Insecta" family="Tortricidae" genus="Chimoptesis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="207" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="miniaula">
<emphasis box="[776,876,835,859]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="207">miniaula</emphasis>
